-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/13103452\/minca-colombia-09.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-4-marinka-waterfall\">4. Marinka Waterfall<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cascada Marinka (Marinka Waterfall) is one of the most popular things to do in Minca. Surrounded by dense green jungle, discover this beautiful waterfall (with both upper and lower falls) and a massive pool at the base for swimming. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5.jpg\" alt=\"minca colombia things to do Marinka Waterfall\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"minca colombia things to do Marinka Waterfall\" class=\"wp-image-87299 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Up this high, the water is exceptionally refreshing, making it the perfect spot to cool off after a long jungle hike. Plus, this lush natural park also has huge hanging nets for relaxing and taking in the sounds and sights of nature.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Make sure to take a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reef-safe-sunscreen\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">reef-safe sunscreen<\/a> and mosquito repellent! There is a restaurant and toilet within the park. However, if you choose to bring your own food, please remember to remove your rubbish.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17.jpg\" alt=\"getting to Marinka Waterfall minca colombia\"><\/noscript><img alt=\"getting to Marinka Waterfall minca colombia\" class=\"wp-image-88274 lazypreload\" width=\"241\" height=\"338\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 839px) 100vw, 839px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17.jpg 1370w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-428x600.jpg 428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-578x810.jpg 578w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-241x338.jpg 241w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-548x768.jpg 548w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-731x1024.jpg 731w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-771x1080.jpg 771w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-1028x1440.jpg 1028w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-300x420.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-600x841.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-150x210.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165026\/minca-colombia-17.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-getting-to-marinka-waterfall\">Getting to Marinka Waterfall<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The falls are an hour&#x2019;s walk from the village, which is doable, but it can get very hot during the day. Otherwise, you can take a motorbike taxi for around 15 minutes, costing 10,000 COP each way (2.50 USD). <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18.jpg\" alt=\"swim Marinka Waterfall minca colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"swim Marinka Waterfall minca colombia\" class=\"wp-image-88276 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1363px) 100vw, 1363px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18.jpg 1363w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-426x600.jpg 426w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-575x810.jpg 575w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-240x338.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-545x768.jpg 545w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-727x1024.jpg 727w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-767x1080.jpg 767w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-1022x1440.jpg 1022w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-300x423.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-600x845.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-150x211.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When you arrive, pay 5000 COP (1.25 USD) to enter before embarking on a beautiful garden walkway that will take you through the jungle to the falls. We recommend arriving as early as possible to avoid the crowds, as from 10 AM it will get very busy.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>When you return to the entrance, motorbike taxis will take you back to town. Alternatively, you can carry on further uphill to Sierra Minca for sunset.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-minca\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Minca.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19.jpg\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia motorbike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia motorbike\" class=\"wp-image-88380 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140931\/minca-colombia-19.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21.jpg\" alt=\"minca colombia Marinka Waterfall \"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"minca colombia Marinka Waterfall \" class=\"wp-image-88386 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22141017\/minca-colombia-21.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-5-blue-lagoon\">5. Blue Lagoon<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Blue Lagoon (Pozo Azul) is another excellent day trip from Minca. Plus, it&#x2019;s free to enter! However, be aware that it&#x2019;s always busy as many tour groups come here. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you arrive, you&#x2019;ll see a few small falls and pools which are great for swimming, although prepare yourself for the biting cold temperatures of the mountain water. There is also a swing at the main pool, which guarantees plenty of fun for visitors. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Getting to Blue Lagoon<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Blue Lagoon is just over an hour&#x2019;s walk from Minca and is on the way to Finca la Victoria (we recommend visiting on the way back from your tour for a nice refreshing dip). Alternatively, take a taxi for 10,000 COP each way (2.50 USD).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-6-go-hiking\">6. Go Hiking<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are lots of incredible hikes you can do around Minca. The most popular is the Los Pinos Trail which gives you a magical view over the Sierra Nevada mountains. You will hike for 6 hours, with the first 3 hours dedicated to an uphill climb! Once at the top, though, it is all worth it for the magical views you&#x2019;ll get over the green landscape.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23.jpg\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia hiking\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia hiking\" class=\"wp-image-88414 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-150x194.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Up for a bit more of an adventure? The Cerro Kennedy hike is one of the top things to do in Minca (a 2-day walk with one overnight stay). The path will take you incredibly high (3100 meters above sea level), so as you can imagine, the views are unbeatable! At the summit, you&#x2019;ll even see the snow-capped peaks of Pico Colon and Pico Bolivar in the distance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-7-see-minca-village\">7. See Minca Village<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Minca village is tiny (only 600 people live in the entire town) with not a huge amount to see. However, that&#x2019;s the beauty of Minca; it&#x2019;s a place to relax, unwind and enjoy the beauty of nature. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143424\/minca-colombia-6.jpg\" alt=\"minca colombia street art\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"minca colombia street art\" class=\"wp-image-87310 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143424\/minca-colombia-6.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143424\/minca-colombia-6-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\