wever, if you have some time, head to the main street, where you&#x2019;ll find some cute restaurants and handicraft shops where you can buy souvenirs from your trip.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-minca\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Minca.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143729\/minca-colombia-1.jpg\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia shopping\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia shopping\" class=\"wp-image-87312 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143729\/minca-colombia-1.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143729\/minca-colombia-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143729\/minca-colombia-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143729\/minca-colombia-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143729\/minca-colombia-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143729\/minca-colombia-1-109x163.jpg 109