a-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/11143753\/minca-colombia-3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-8-day-trip-to-tayrona-national-park\">8. Day Trip to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/tayrona-national-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tayrona National Park<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Only a 50-60 minute drive away is the magical <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/tayrona-national-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tayrona National Park<\/a>, bordering the Caribbean coastline. For paradise island beaches, this is the place to go! You&#x2019;ll find white sand, clear turquoise water, and small huts and hammocks where you can camp under the stars. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10.jpg\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia Tayrona national park day trip\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia Tayrona national park day trip\" class=\"wp-image-85278 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinour