><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Always check reviews of restaurants in Minca because the town has some water problems. Consider bringing your own water filter to refill your water bottle and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">travel plastic-free<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4.jpg\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia best restaurants\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia best restaurants\" class=\"wp-image-87304 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142940\/minca-colombia-4-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com