 that as you&#x2019;re going up into the mountains, the roads can become very twisty (top tip for those with motion sickness!).&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The other option is to take a shared taxi (colectivo) from Estacion de Minca (Calle 12, Carrerra 9). The price is around 9,000 COP (2.25 USD) per person and is the only other transport option from Santa Marta, as there is no public bus route.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--flight \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--flight\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-santa-marta\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your flight to Santa Marta<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140953\/minca-colombia-20.jpg\" alt=\"how to get to Marinka Waterfall minca colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to get to Marinka Waterfall minca colombia\" class=\"wp-image-88383 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1284px) 100vw, 1284px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140953\/minca-colombia-20.jpg 1284w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140953\/minca-colombia-20-401x600.jpg 401w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140953\/minca-colombia-20-542x810.jpg 542w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22140953