ing a motorcycle. You can rent them yourself (for approximately 100,000 COP (24 USD) a day), but it&#x2019;s easier to jump on the motorcycle taxis, which will pick you up from the center of town and take you wherever you need to go. Prices are fairly reasonable, and it&#x2019;s usually easier than hiking uphill in the heat.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>If you don&#x2019;t mind a bit of hiking, everything is walkable in Minca. Just prepare for uphill walks, and always bring plenty of water, mosquito repellent, and sunscreen. Be aware that depending on the weather, the paths can be muddy (rainy season) or dry and dusty (dry season).<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-minca\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Minca.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"budget\">How Much Does Minca Cost?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As Minca is on the Colombia backpacker trail, prices are very reasonable, with plenty of budget hostels that still come with amazing pools and amenities. Remember, you&#x2019;ll need to allocate money for motorcycle taxis to take you to your hostel or on various day trips in the area.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Please note that there are no official ATMs in Minca, so bring enough cash with you to last the duration of your stay.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2.jpg\" alt=\"minca restaurants colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"minca restaurants colombia\" class=\"wp-image-88420 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143213\/minca-colombia-2-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.sal